It has been reported that SARS-CoV-2 is sensitive to ultraviolet rays and heat of 56 °C for 30 minutes, ether, ethanol 75%, chlorine-containing disinfectant, prophylactic acid, chloroform, and other fatty solvents other than chlorhexidine, and these can effectively neutralize the virus.
